ModalBoxHelper v.1.0
====================

# Author:: Millisami
# WebSite:: http://millisami.info
# Based on Modalbox Js Library
To complete the installation, run the following rake task:

rake modalbox:setup

This Modalbox Helper is based on the javascript at http://www.wildbit.com/labs/modalbox/

Note: this js use Prototype JavaScript framework, version 1.6.0 and script.aculo.us 1.8.0 library

You must add the stylesheet, so add the following line on your page head of your layout:

<%= stylesheet_link_tag 'modalbox' %>

The is very simple to add a Modalbox in your page add this:
<%= modalbox_link_to(name, options = {}, html_options = {}, *parameters_for_method_reference) %>

Example:
<%= modalbox_link_to 'New project via Modalbox', { :url => new_project_path, :width => "500" }, :title => 'New Project' %>

